            <bioghist>
                <p>The United States Insurance Company was chartered in 1810 and dealt in marine
                    insurance.</p>
            </bioghist>

            <scopecontent>
                <p>The collection includes letters from and especially to Israel Pleasants,
                    president of the company, regarding marine insurance claims due to damages,
                    capture, and detention of ships.</p>
            </scopecontent>


